WEBVTT

01:50.160 --> 01:53.950
[Love Between Lines]

01:54.200 --> 01:56.800
[Episode 3]

02:00.480 --> 02:02.340
Welcome to our park's gathering.

02:02.510 --> 02:04.000
We've had
several new stores open recently.

02:04.000 --> 02:05.510
It's a good chance for you all
to get to know each other.

02:05.510 --> 02:06.870
What took you so long?

02:12.360 --> 02:13.360
Hello everyone.

02:13.590 --> 02:14.960
I'm Xiaorou's husband.

02:14.960 --> 02:16.150
Just call me Guangming.

02:16.150 --> 02:16.750
Mr. Ming.

02:16.750 --> 02:17.560
No, no, no.

02:18.310 --> 02:19.590
I work in software development.

02:19.590 --> 02:20.680
Come, have a seat.

02:22.000 --> 02:23.120
Have a seat.

02:23.120 --> 02:24.120
Scoot in a little.

02:28.520 --> 02:29.980
Did you order enough food?

02:30.270 --> 02:31.360
Is everyone here?

02:31.710 --> 02:32.430
Well,

02:32.630 --> 02:34.630
the owner of ME Club, Mr. Gong, is busy.

02:34.630 --> 02:36.380
He said some staff would come instead.

02:36.380 --> 02:37.690
Your wife's shop
is just across the street.

02:37.690 --> 02:38.590
You should know that.

02:38.590 --> 02:39.190
Right?

02:39.310 --> 02:40.590
Those NPCs at their shop

02:40.590 --> 02:42.079
are quite famous online.

02:42.430 --> 02:43.360
NPCs?

02:43.520 --> 02:45.400
Will Qin Xiaoyi come?

02:45.800 --> 02:47.079
Qin Xiaoyi?

02:47.310 --> 02:48.030
Oh, right.

02:48.120 --> 02:50.079
Is he the one who plays General Qin?

02:50.150 --> 02:51.000
He should be coming.

02:51.000 --> 02:52.600
He's really popular lately.

02:52.870 --> 02:53.520
Is that so?

02:53.750 --> 02:54.840
Then let's organize a game next time.

02:54.840 --> 02:55.680
Sounds good.

02:56.560 --> 02:58.360
I'm going outside to make a call.

02:59.590 --> 03:00.590
Come on, Mr. Ming.

03:00.870 --> 03:02.150
Let's have a drink.

03:06.750 --> 03:08.570
[Educational Background] [Work Experience]
[Main Responsibilities]

03:16.990 --> 03:19.970
[Resume]

03:23.240 --> 03:25.900
Writing a resume
is about organizing yourself.

03:26.190 --> 03:28.400
This chicken soup for the soul
is really good.

03:28.400 --> 03:29.150
I get you.

03:29.430 --> 03:31.280
I feel like my previous experience
isn't relevant,

03:31.280 --> 03:33.740
but if I don't include it,
it would be a waste.

03:33.870 --> 03:35.870
This person really understands me.

03:36.000 --> 03:37.079
Why not join the group chat party

03:37.079 --> 03:38.750
and ask everyone for some advice?

03:38.750 --> 03:40.280
That's an idea.

03:40.280 --> 03:41.840
When you're stuck, take a break

03:41.840 --> 03:43.300
and have something sweet.

03:43.960 --> 03:45.620
This one makes the most sense.

03:53.840 --> 03:54.360
Zhao,

03:54.360 --> 03:56.000
I was just about to call you.

03:56.329 --> 03:57.440
Are you at the café?

03:58.120 --> 03:59.400
Star Club 888.

04:00.240 --> 04:00.800
What?

04:01.150 --> 04:02.750
I'm at Room 888 in Star Club.

04:02.960 --> 04:04.470
Qin Xiaoyi will be here soon.

04:04.470 --> 04:05.670
You should come over.

04:06.400 --> 04:07.630
Haven't you been checking his sessions

04:07.630 --> 04:08.750
at the murder mystery game place every day

04:08.750 --> 04:10.190
just for him?

04:10.630 --> 04:12.030
Come over and ask him yourself.

04:12.030 --> 04:12.870
Set up another game

04:12.870 --> 04:13.930
directly with him.

04:14.910 --> 04:15.870
Wait for me.

04:27.310 --> 04:28.000
Xiu!

04:28.270 --> 04:28.950
Over here!

04:31.720 --> 04:32.470
Li Yue.

04:34.720 --> 04:35.390
Li Yue.

04:39.000 --> 04:40.120
Let me introduce you.

04:40.120 --> 04:40.630
This is Li Yue,

04:40.630 --> 04:42.430
a junior in the Drama Academy's
Acting Department.

04:42.430 --> 04:43.870
And this is my bestie, Hu Xiu.

04:43.870 --> 04:44.720
Hello.

04:44.900 --> 04:46.240
Your name's pretty interesting.

04:46.240 --> 04:47.190
I heard you also like coming to

04:47.190 --> 04:48.650
our murder mystery games.

04:49.040 --> 04:50.159
Don't just stand there.

04:50.159 --> 04:50.560
Have a seat.

04:50.560 --> 04:51.490
Yes, have a seat.

05:00.510 --> 05:02.270
Then you'll be our VIP from now on.

05:02.270 --> 05:03.630
My win rate hasn't been great lately.

05:03.630 --> 05:05.290
Come help me when you're free.

05:05.680 --> 05:06.630
I'll try my best.

05:07.270 --> 05:08.530
Can I add you on WeChat?

05:16.190 --> 05:16.720
Li Yue,

05:16.800 --> 05:18.040
let's exchange WeChat too.

05:18.040 --> 05:18.270
Sure.

05:18.270 --> 05:19.680
I heard your murder mystery games
are really fun.

05:19.680 --> 05:21.310
If Li Yue is here,

05:21.830 --> 05:22.800
then...

05:29.750 --> 05:31.830
Today's latest murder mystery game

05:32.180 --> 05:34.040
should be Group A with Qin Xiaoyi.

05:36.310 --> 05:36.870
Xiu.

05:37.270 --> 05:38.240
Where are you going?

05:38.240 --> 05:39.000
I have something to do.

05:39.000 --> 05:40.000
I'll be going now.

05:42.000 --> 05:42.630
Zhao,

05:42.920 --> 05:43.920
I think you

05:44.310 --> 05:46.510
have a serious case of face-blindness.

05:46.800 --> 05:47.390
Bye.

05:58.560 --> 06:00.020
I can still make it, right?

06:00.720 --> 06:01.310
Alright.

06:01.830 --> 06:02.430
Excuse me.

06:02.600 --> 06:03.430
You're late.

06:03.560 --> 06:05.020
There are no choices left.

06:05.750 --> 06:07.510
The character doesn't matter.
The outcome does.

06:07.510 --> 06:08.030
Okay.

06:08.240 --> 06:09.240
This way, please.

06:10.010 --> 06:12.890
You are Wu Jin,
the investigation expert sent by Side S.

06:10.960 --> 06:12.280
[Wu Jin, Investigation Expert]

06:13.600 --> 06:15.660
Your mission is to find the old mayor,

06:16.230 --> 06:17.360
get the command token,

06:17.360 --> 06:19.560
and help the new mayor you support
take office.

06:19.560 --> 06:20.430
Remember,

06:20.600 --> 06:23.190
your choices determine your fate.

06:23.750 --> 06:25.000
Find the old mayor?

06:25.390 --> 06:26.870
In previous games,

06:27.000 --> 06:29.200
the old mayor was always assassinated.

06:29.430 --> 06:30.630
How come this time...

06:40.600 --> 06:43.390
If finding the command token
and the old mayor is the only way

06:43.390 --> 06:45.450
to make the new city lord take office,

06:45.480 --> 06:46.560
Qin Xiaoyi

06:46.560 --> 06:49.000
must also be investigating
with all his efforts.

06:49.000 --> 06:50.159
There must be clues

06:50.360 --> 06:51.600
in his office.

06:58.600 --> 06:59.600
The police are also

06:59.600 --> 07:02.000
investigating
the old mayor's disappearance.

07:02.000 --> 07:03.800
There's been no progress so far.

07:04.800 --> 07:05.660
Keep watching.

07:07.390 --> 07:08.190
Any leads on that key?

07:08.190 --> 07:09.590
He's really in this game?

07:09.830 --> 07:12.160
We caught a suspicious person at the café.

07:12.310 --> 07:15.240
She said the key
was deposited at the Central Hotel.

07:18.040 --> 07:18.920
Bai Luoyu?

07:20.800 --> 07:23.120
She usually only trades information
for money

07:23.120 --> 07:25.310
and doesn't get involved
in anything in Rongcheng.

07:25.310 --> 07:26.640
No wonder we missed her.

07:27.600 --> 07:29.070
Do we need to...

07:29.680 --> 07:30.410
Who's there?

07:55.430 --> 07:56.430
How can I help...

07:59.920 --> 08:02.380
Give me the key
to the old mayor's residence.

08:16.120 --> 08:16.950
I never saw this house before

08:16.950 --> 08:18.360
in this game.

08:22.310 --> 08:23.070
Never mind.

08:23.800 --> 08:25.200
I'll go in and take a look.

08:39.909 --> 08:41.270
Ten years ago,

08:41.390 --> 08:43.789
the whole family committed suicide here.

08:44.600 --> 08:46.600
This place is eerily strange.

08:46.910 --> 08:49.480
I think this is a haunted house.

08:53.240 --> 08:54.270
No way.

09:34.280 --> 09:36.010
The old mayor's command token?

09:46.760 --> 09:47.720
Hurry, hurry.

09:56.200 --> 09:57.550
Don't mess with me.

09:59.510 --> 10:00.710
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

10:01.080 --> 10:03.010
I'll just take the token and leave.

10:12.270 --> 10:13.470
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

10:31.270 --> 10:32.200
Don't come over.

11:04.550 --> 11:05.320
Are you okay?

11:05.840 --> 11:06.600
Get up.

11:07.480 --> 11:09.290
My legs are shaking.

11:10.440 --> 11:11.440
Sorry about that.

11:11.600 --> 11:12.870
It's a new haunted house setting.

11:12.870 --> 11:13.870
Did it scare you?

11:14.630 --> 11:15.270
There...

11:15.480 --> 11:16.790
There's a...

11:19.360 --> 11:23.310
♪ I moved closer to you,
and you moved closer to me ♪

11:23.730 --> 11:27.460
♪ The motionless night began to shimmer ♪

11:27.940 --> 11:32.220
♪ The fireworks bear witness, as if ♪

11:31.630 --> 11:33.150
What is this?

11:32.480 --> 11:35.710
♪ they're waiting for the words
we want to say ♪

11:36.170 --> 11:39.460
♪ I moved closer to you,
and you moved closer to me ♪

11:38.360 --> 11:39.560
Spring in Rongcheng.

11:40.670 --> 11:45.960
♪ It felt as if two lonely islands
had finally ♪

11:46.600 --> 11:51.210
♪ Getting closer and slipped into
the flow of time together ♪

11:48.000 --> 11:49.720
Do you think it's romantic, having petals

11:49.720 --> 11:51.250
fall from the sky like this?

11:52.550 --> 11:54.150
The game is designed this way.

11:54.150 --> 11:55.680
It has nothing to do with me.

11:58.520 --> 12:00.000
I can walk by myself.

12:00.670 --> 12:02.440
I was just sitting too long

12:02.440 --> 12:03.640
and my legs went numb.

12:04.030 --> 12:04.910
I'll take it slow.

12:04.910 --> 12:05.790
If you're in a hurry,

12:05.790 --> 12:07.030
you can go ahead.

12:08.000 --> 12:10.270
To get out,
you must go through the garden.

12:10.270 --> 12:12.390
Those things will definitely appear again.

12:12.390 --> 12:13.910
You know how it feels

12:14.030 --> 12:15.090
to encounter them.

12:15.790 --> 12:16.750
Are you sure

12:17.000 --> 12:18.060
you can do it alone?

12:19.840 --> 12:20.550
Of course.

12:28.080 --> 12:29.740
Who said she could do it alone?

12:31.240 --> 12:33.390
You're just too slow.

12:33.750 --> 12:35.480
Look, I've already passed you.

12:48.360 --> 12:49.200
Ms. Wu,

12:50.240 --> 12:52.110
you're doing this on purpose, aren't you?

12:52.110 --> 12:53.350
They're all here.

12:58.480 --> 13:01.080
Pretend you don't see them
and go straight through.

13:01.080 --> 13:02.080
Where's your gun?

13:02.960 --> 13:03.480
Why?

13:04.510 --> 13:07.270
I want to see the petals falling again.

13:08.510 --> 13:10.750
Who just criticized this design?

13:19.120 --> 13:20.360
Th-th-this one.

13:35.510 --> 13:36.720
Fireflies!

13:45.630 --> 13:46.510
Th-that one is big.

13:46.510 --> 13:47.370
Shoot that one.

14:04.720 --> 14:06.030
There's another one.

14:06.030 --> 14:07.440
That one. That one.

14:08.840 --> 14:10.000
Why did you stop?

14:11.270 --> 14:11.870
I'm tired.

14:14.290 --> 14:15.270
I thought

14:15.270 --> 14:17.120
General Qin was supposed to be amazing

14:17.120 --> 14:18.200
with weapons.

14:18.420 --> 14:20.350
But your stamina is quite limited.

14:24.000 --> 14:25.270
And these effects—

14:25.270 --> 14:27.070
they have no originality at all.

14:27.390 --> 14:28.240
Ms. Wu,

14:28.630 --> 14:30.830
reverse psychology doesn't work on me.

14:32.470 --> 14:33.600
I'll play by myself.

14:34.360 --> 14:36.200
Ms. Wu, don't you have your own weapon?

14:36.200 --> 14:37.550
Why take someone else's?

14:37.550 --> 14:38.240
I...

14:38.240 --> 14:39.840
Why are you being so stingy?

14:39.840 --> 14:41.030
Just let me play with it for a while.

14:41.030 --> 14:41.670
No.

14:44.630 --> 14:45.690
We're already out.

14:46.670 --> 14:47.070
Yes.

14:47.320 --> 14:48.750
I kicked the door open.

14:49.670 --> 14:50.600
That passage is unusable now.

14:50.600 --> 14:51.330
Close it off.

14:51.420 --> 14:53.600
Don't let anyone go through there anymore.

14:53.600 --> 14:54.080
Well...

14:56.630 --> 14:57.720
What happened?

15:00.270 --> 15:00.840
Nothing.

15:05.440 --> 15:07.150
General Qin, you reminded me.

15:07.440 --> 15:08.840
I'm also armed.

15:12.440 --> 15:13.270
Now,

15:13.290 --> 15:15.020
answer my questions honestly.

15:15.260 --> 15:18.460
Why did you suddenly appear
at the old mayor's residence?

15:19.510 --> 15:20.870
Didn't you just hear?

15:20.910 --> 15:22.030
The control center alerted me

15:22.030 --> 15:23.640
that a player was in trouble
at the haunted house,

15:23.640 --> 15:24.690
so I went to check.

15:24.870 --> 15:26.150
If you want to leave now,

15:26.150 --> 15:27.280
you can get a refund.

15:28.200 --> 15:29.620
The Military Affairs Office...

15:29.620 --> 15:31.420
is quite far from here, isn't it?

15:31.720 --> 15:34.360
Why were you the farthest away,

15:34.360 --> 15:35.820
yet arrived the quickest?

15:39.690 --> 15:41.750
Because when I received the message,

15:41.840 --> 15:43.150
I was already here.

15:43.600 --> 15:44.360
I heard from Bai Luoyu

15:44.360 --> 15:46.220
that a female player took the key.

15:46.540 --> 15:48.470
Although I didn't know who took it,

15:49.080 --> 15:50.740
the only thing I was certain of

15:51.200 --> 15:52.060
was that person

15:52.170 --> 15:53.700
would definitely go there.

15:55.630 --> 15:56.840
What exactly is it

15:56.840 --> 15:58.670
that's worth such a risk, Ms. Wu?

15:59.270 --> 16:01.270
Haven't you already figured it out?

16:04.950 --> 16:06.550
Without this command token,

16:06.550 --> 16:08.910
you absolutely cannot become the mayor.

16:09.840 --> 16:11.880
Since you saved me just now,

16:11.910 --> 16:13.060
I'll use this token

16:13.290 --> 16:14.600
to make a deal with you.

16:15.390 --> 16:16.250
I'm listening.

16:18.270 --> 16:19.200
I want to know

16:19.200 --> 16:20.270
who Jiang Yi is.

16:23.390 --> 16:25.630
So Jiang Yi works for Feng Youjin?

16:28.000 --> 16:29.200
Ning Zechen found out

16:29.370 --> 16:32.030
that Jiang Yi
was once the Feng family's butler.

16:33.360 --> 16:34.360
It's almost dawn.

16:34.360 --> 16:35.260
We're running out of time.

16:35.260 --> 16:36.660
Let's go check upstairs.

16:38.020 --> 16:38.970
Ms. Sun,

16:39.000 --> 16:41.130
it's been a pleasure working with you.

16:41.960 --> 16:42.620
Be careful.

16:46.530 --> 16:47.590
What's that sound?

16:52.200 --> 16:52.750
This way,

16:53.150 --> 16:53.670
please.

16:55.150 --> 16:56.350
It's been a pleasure.

16:58.040 --> 16:58.840
They're gone.

17:02.840 --> 17:04.349
Since the mayor has been hidden away,

17:04.349 --> 17:05.960
it must be somewhere secret.

17:12.000 --> 17:12.640
Look.

17:14.109 --> 17:16.270
These four rooms are all the same size,

17:16.270 --> 17:17.640
but when we checked earlier,

17:16.740 --> 17:19.349
[Partial View of the Rongcheng
Finance Department]

17:17.640 --> 17:20.160
these two
were clearly smaller than the others.

17:20.160 --> 17:21.690
There's a hidden room here.

17:22.030 --> 17:23.230
Let's go check again.

17:28.349 --> 17:29.480
35.

17:30.200 --> 17:30.830
What?

17:31.060 --> 17:32.890
The previous room had 56 floor tiles,

17:32.890 --> 17:34.690
but this room only has 35.

17:35.030 --> 17:36.130
If there's a secret room,

17:36.130 --> 17:37.660
there must be a secret door.

17:50.110 --> 17:51.440
Why aren't you helping?

17:51.590 --> 17:52.740
I don't know these things.

17:52.740 --> 17:53.680
Otherwise, I would have noticed

17:53.680 --> 17:55.340
the difference in room sizes.

17:55.570 --> 17:57.960
Yeah, all you do is talk.

18:03.390 --> 18:04.790
Lightweight materials?

18:10.230 --> 18:12.030
A movable wall?

18:12.820 --> 18:14.820
This designer was really thorough.

18:31.180 --> 18:32.250
Old mayor?

18:33.550 --> 18:34.400
Go untie him.

18:39.070 --> 18:40.000
It's in the back.

18:41.590 --> 18:43.850
Thank goodness we found you before dawn.

18:46.130 --> 18:47.200
Almost done.

18:47.600 --> 18:48.230
Done.

18:54.220 --> 18:55.020
Ms. Wu,

18:55.610 --> 18:57.090
thank you for saving me.

19:12.940 --> 19:14.690
Qin Xiaoyi, you bastard!

19:16.180 --> 19:17.830
Y-you're so devious!

19:17.850 --> 19:18.850
Let me go!

19:19.360 --> 19:20.220
You flatter me.

19:23.830 --> 19:25.240
Saving me in that haunted house

19:25.240 --> 19:27.300
was also part of your plan, wasn't it?

19:27.510 --> 19:28.790
I already told you

19:29.720 --> 19:31.650
to quit the game
and that we'd give you a refund,

19:31.650 --> 19:32.650
but you refused.

19:33.250 --> 19:35.100
I'd rather lose than run away.

19:36.480 --> 19:37.210
Don't worry.

19:37.820 --> 19:38.880
You can't run away.

19:40.270 --> 19:41.360
Because...

19:45.400 --> 19:47.510
a fox can't be the winner here.

19:52.000 --> 19:53.090
Goodbye, Ms. Wu.

19:53.550 --> 19:54.830
Qin Xiaoyi...

19:55.980 --> 19:56.810
Qin Xiaoyi!

19:57.590 --> 19:59.320
Qin Xiaoyi, let's talk this...

20:10.270 --> 20:11.640
Qin Xiaoyi!

20:14.810 --> 20:15.870
Congratulations.

20:20.370 --> 20:21.680
He really lives up to his name.

20:21.680 --> 20:23.050
Great. That's awesome.

20:23.350 --> 20:24.400
Impressive.

20:34.030 --> 20:36.590
The new version's virtual atmosphere
is amazing.

20:36.590 --> 20:37.790
I like the thrill.

20:37.790 --> 20:39.590
Otherwise, it would get boring.

20:40.600 --> 20:41.140
I was wrong, sir.

20:41.140 --> 20:42.700
It would never get boring.

20:48.310 --> 20:49.420
What's up? Something's wrong?

20:49.420 --> 20:50.210
I think

20:50.400 --> 20:51.960
the randomly triggered horror missions

20:51.960 --> 20:53.300
aren't very appropriate.

20:53.300 --> 20:55.820
We should assign them to players
with higher tolerance first.

20:55.820 --> 20:56.410
Well...

20:56.440 --> 20:58.190
thanks for your help
with that last session.

20:58.190 --> 20:59.560
That girl has played several times.

20:59.560 --> 21:01.240
I thought she was a veteran player.

21:01.240 --> 21:01.680
Here's the thing.

21:01.680 --> 21:04.110
This is the first run of the new version.

21:04.550 --> 21:05.070
Did you inform

21:05.070 --> 21:06.440
all players about the horror segments

21:06.440 --> 21:07.830
before they entered?

21:09.000 --> 21:10.110
She came late

21:10.110 --> 21:11.480
and was in a hurry,

21:11.480 --> 21:12.590
so I just...

21:14.920 --> 21:15.450
Alright.

21:15.720 --> 21:16.750
Well...

21:16.920 --> 21:18.550
I'll adjust the trigger mode

21:18.550 --> 21:19.910
for the horror missions.

21:19.910 --> 21:21.500
Let's pause them for now.

21:21.680 --> 21:24.140
I'll go back
and give the team more training.

21:24.350 --> 21:25.080
I'm leaving.

22:05.830 --> 22:06.720
Use mine.

22:06.720 --> 22:08.120
My ride will be here soon.

22:09.880 --> 22:10.470
Thanks.

22:18.350 --> 22:19.350
So annoying.

22:19.960 --> 22:21.440
School starts tomorrow.

22:21.440 --> 22:23.440
I haven't even finished my lab report yet.

22:23.440 --> 22:25.510
What have you been doing
this entire vacation?

22:25.510 --> 22:26.740
Playing murder mystery games.

22:26.740 --> 22:27.840
It's really addictive.

22:27.840 --> 22:29.750
If someone could write my report for me,

22:29.750 --> 22:32.010
I'll immediately support them as mayor.

22:32.400 --> 22:33.880
Life isn't a murder mystery game.

22:33.880 --> 22:35.480
Don't get too caught up in it.

22:39.350 --> 22:40.280
The ride is here.

22:40.440 --> 22:41.030
Let's go.

22:53.680 --> 22:54.590
Yeah,

22:55.240 --> 22:57.240
we always have to return to reality.

23:20.100 --> 23:21.100
Are you home now?

23:23.530 --> 23:24.750
Just letting you know,

23:24.750 --> 23:26.160
the club has sent an apology message

23:26.160 --> 23:28.310
to that female player who got scared

23:28.340 --> 23:30.400
and gave her some free game vouchers.

23:31.590 --> 23:32.200
Got it.

23:32.510 --> 23:32.990
By the way,

23:32.990 --> 23:34.070
I heard from the receptionist

23:34.070 --> 23:36.220
that she had specifically
asked about your sessions before.

23:36.220 --> 23:37.750
What a coincidence, right?

23:42.160 --> 23:43.190
Anything else?

23:43.890 --> 23:44.400
Nope.

23:44.750 --> 23:45.810
Get some rest then.

24:00.890 --> 24:01.650
Take care.

24:01.960 --> 24:02.740
Thank you.

24:08.840 --> 24:09.970
Your stomach hurts?

24:10.780 --> 24:12.310
Did you forget to eat again?

24:14.100 --> 24:16.700
Seems like I got too busy last night
and forgot.

24:31.880 --> 24:34.840
You need a healthy stomach to work well,
Ms. Hu.

24:39.070 --> 24:40.800
Things aren't going smoothly?

24:44.030 --> 24:46.450
I've asked a friend in headhunting
to keep an eye out.

24:46.450 --> 24:48.080
He told me to tweak my resume a bit,

24:48.080 --> 24:50.560
lean more toward architectural design.

24:50.930 --> 24:53.530
The most impressive part
of my resume right now

24:53.790 --> 24:55.750
is just my relevant college major.

24:56.590 --> 24:58.790
And I didn't pursue further education.

25:00.960 --> 25:02.550
Since graduating,

25:02.580 --> 25:04.180
I've been running this café.

25:04.410 --> 25:05.920
I've never worked elsewhere.

25:05.920 --> 25:07.780
I can't give you any great advice.

25:09.130 --> 25:10.610
But...

25:12.350 --> 25:13.240
I think your resume...

25:13.240 --> 25:14.960
might be a bit too plain.

25:15.310 --> 25:16.110
In the architecture industry,

25:16.110 --> 25:17.780
everything is already quite dull.

25:17.780 --> 25:20.460
There's no need for fancy stuff.

25:21.350 --> 25:22.240
But doesn't your industry

25:22.240 --> 25:23.920
have plenty of fancy things?

25:24.240 --> 25:25.400
That D something—

25:25.400 --> 25:26.400
isn't it quite fancy?

25:26.400 --> 25:27.310
Dynamism?

25:28.070 --> 25:29.510
They're really excellent.

25:29.510 --> 25:31.920
That popular café on Jianguo West Road

25:31.990 --> 25:33.870
and that super photogenic
Galaxy Bookstore?

25:33.870 --> 25:35.080
Both of them were designed by them.

25:35.080 --> 25:36.940
How do you know so much about them?

25:37.750 --> 25:39.400
After all,
it's the top architectural studio

25:39.400 --> 25:40.940
in the industry these past two years.

25:40.940 --> 25:41.840
They have so many awards.

25:41.840 --> 25:43.640
It's hard not to know about them.

25:45.550 --> 25:47.350
I should get back to job hunting.

25:47.790 --> 25:48.790
Forget about dreams.

25:48.790 --> 25:50.400
My wallet is empty.

25:51.350 --> 25:52.110
Xiu.

25:53.260 --> 25:56.220
Maybe you should consider
other income sources.

25:56.880 --> 25:58.940
Isn't that attic at your place empty?

25:59.030 --> 26:00.110
Rent it out.

26:10.260 --> 26:10.910
Cai.

26:11.190 --> 26:12.110
Hu?

26:13.280 --> 26:15.000
You stayed up late again last night,
didn't you?

26:15.000 --> 26:16.870
Look at those dark circles
under your eyes.

26:16.870 --> 26:18.500
Job hunting is exhausting.

26:18.770 --> 26:19.380
What?

26:20.230 --> 26:20.950
I said

26:21.200 --> 26:21.920
working is exhausting.

26:21.920 --> 26:23.520
Your job is much better, Cai.

26:24.020 --> 26:25.150
Nonsense.

26:30.670 --> 26:31.260
Wait.

26:32.160 --> 26:32.680
You...

26:32.860 --> 26:33.900
I got it fir-

27:00.640 --> 27:02.440
Pretending not to know me again?

27:04.880 --> 27:05.550
Thanks.

27:38.240 --> 27:39.640
Why are you following me?

27:39.640 --> 27:40.570
What do you want?

27:40.940 --> 27:42.140
Who's following you?

27:42.560 --> 27:44.270
Ms. Hu, you're back?

27:47.330 --> 27:49.040
Excuse me, let me through.

27:52.070 --> 27:52.930
It's over here.

27:58.640 --> 28:00.440
Still pretending not to know me?

28:00.920 --> 28:02.780
Who's taking this too seriously?

28:06.790 --> 28:08.050
Signing the contract?

28:08.100 --> 28:08.660
Mom,

28:08.960 --> 28:11.350
why are you trying to
rent out the house again?

28:11.350 --> 28:12.580
This house can't be rented.

28:12.580 --> 28:13.450
I don't agree.

28:14.210 --> 28:15.600
Please help me ask around again.

28:15.600 --> 28:16.350
Please do me a favor.

28:16.350 --> 28:16.950
Thank you.

28:18.900 --> 28:20.370
There aren't many houses for rent here,

28:20.370 --> 28:22.400
but I asked my colleagues
to keep an eye out.

28:22.400 --> 28:23.180
Once there's news,

28:23.180 --> 28:24.910
I'll let you know immediately.

28:32.650 --> 28:33.650
Nonsense!

28:33.680 --> 28:35.640
How dare you trick my mom
into renting out the house?

28:35.640 --> 28:37.600
How dare you offend me, Chen Dabao?

28:37.880 --> 28:40.080
Let's see who still dares to rent to him.

28:40.600 --> 28:41.930
Borrowing my pot again?

28:44.640 --> 28:46.510
Dazhong, lend me two cucumbers.

29:08.720 --> 29:09.680
As you know,

29:09.840 --> 29:12.160
most of the residents here are elderly,

29:12.210 --> 29:13.440
and they've lived here

29:13.440 --> 29:15.030
for most of their lives.

29:15.810 --> 29:17.650
They don't like moving around.

29:18.440 --> 29:19.640
Money isn't an issue.

29:19.880 --> 29:20.680
I understand.

29:20.790 --> 29:22.680
I've tried offering higher rent.

29:22.880 --> 29:23.500
It's just that

29:23.500 --> 29:26.010
the news about you renting
Granny Chen's house has spread.

29:26.010 --> 29:28.070
That Chen Dabao
has been going around saying

29:28.070 --> 29:29.600
that anyone who rents to you

29:29.600 --> 29:30.660
will be in trouble with him.

29:30.660 --> 29:32.170
Nobody wants to mess with him.

29:32.170 --> 29:33.510
Why don't you try another place?

29:33.510 --> 29:34.070
No.

29:35.310 --> 29:36.640
I'm staying in the lane.

29:41.330 --> 29:43.520
Have you asked about that attic?

29:45.140 --> 29:46.780
You mean Ms. Hu's?

29:46.810 --> 29:48.680
Her rental listing says

29:49.110 --> 29:50.500
"no agents,"

29:50.720 --> 29:52.550
so I can't really ask.

29:52.980 --> 29:53.580
Of course,

29:54.050 --> 29:56.240
you could talk to her yourself.

29:57.440 --> 29:58.170
Got it.

29:58.450 --> 29:59.100
Thanks.

30:07.010 --> 30:07.780
It's all set.

30:08.720 --> 30:09.310
Mr. Zhao

30:09.310 --> 30:10.160
has invested in quite a few

30:10.160 --> 30:11.730
large-scale VR experience centers.

30:11.730 --> 30:13.400
He introduced me to a German company,

30:13.400 --> 30:15.470
saying that a technician named Felix

30:15.580 --> 30:16.330
is really skilled.

30:16.330 --> 30:19.170
If we give him the new scenario,
it'll be no problem at all.

30:19.170 --> 30:19.900
That's good.

30:20.110 --> 30:20.710
By the way,

30:20.930 --> 30:22.570
I also told Mr. Zhao

30:22.840 --> 30:23.350
that in the future,

30:23.350 --> 30:25.880
we could invest in
some VR projects together.

30:26.270 --> 30:26.900
Xiao,

30:27.460 --> 30:28.760
thanks for bringing me here.

30:28.760 --> 30:31.270
Otherwise, I wouldn't even
have a connection with him.

30:31.270 --> 30:32.550
A huge favor like this
can't be thanked enough.

30:32.550 --> 30:34.440
I'll repay you someday.

30:40.030 --> 30:41.360
Don't wait for someday.

30:42.110 --> 30:43.190
Repay it now.

30:46.720 --> 30:47.590
Almost there.

30:48.030 --> 30:48.840
Okay.

30:49.310 --> 30:49.920
Done.

30:50.300 --> 30:51.100
Thank you.

30:52.550 --> 30:54.680
Why did you buy such a big cabinet?

30:55.180 --> 30:57.140
To rent this place out quickly.

30:57.170 --> 30:57.890
Ms. Wu,

30:57.920 --> 31:00.310
are you interested
in the executive GM assistant position?

31:00.310 --> 31:02.000
You should post your rental listing online

31:02.000 --> 31:03.160
more often.

31:03.680 --> 31:04.350
I did.

31:04.680 --> 31:05.890
I post it every day.

31:06.330 --> 31:08.060
Plenty of people contacted me,

31:08.160 --> 31:08.790
but...

31:08.810 --> 31:09.850
half are agents,

31:10.030 --> 31:11.920
and the other half
just asked for basic information

31:11.920 --> 31:13.030
with no follow-up.

31:13.160 --> 31:14.440
So I thought
I'd try to spruce this place up

31:14.440 --> 31:15.880
as soon as possible.

31:17.670 --> 31:18.900
Where should this box be placed?

31:18.900 --> 31:20.700
It's full of your college stuff.

31:21.160 --> 31:22.830
Put it in the living room.

31:23.570 --> 31:25.370
Okay, I'll carry it down for you.

31:26.180 --> 31:26.880
Zhao.

31:27.510 --> 31:29.270
Do you think
I should replace this bed too?

31:29.270 --> 31:31.400
I broke it before and my dad fixed it.

31:33.480 --> 31:35.160
It looks fine to me.

31:35.350 --> 31:36.350
Don't replace it.

31:36.350 --> 31:37.590
What if you keep replacing things

31:37.590 --> 31:38.940
but don't rent it out eventually?

31:38.940 --> 31:39.980
Bah!

31:40.000 --> 31:41.120
I definitely can rent it out.

31:41.120 --> 31:41.940
It'll be rented by tomorrow.

31:41.940 --> 31:44.740
Fine, it'll definitely be rented out
by tomorrow.

31:50.270 --> 31:50.880
Zhao.

31:55.360 --> 31:57.180
[Hello, I'd like to come see the house.]

32:12.990 --> 32:13.640
Hello.

32:16.840 --> 32:18.640
Hi. I'm here to see the house.

32:21.520 --> 32:22.960
Do you mind having a male tenant?

32:22.960 --> 32:24.890
I don't smoke, drink, or keep pets.

32:24.950 --> 32:27.010
And I won't bring random people home.

32:28.010 --> 32:28.820
I don't mind.

32:30.420 --> 32:32.660
This is a two-floor apartment.

32:32.950 --> 32:35.640
This area has a bedroom,
a living room, a kitchen, and a bathroom.

32:35.640 --> 32:36.990
This is the common area.

32:40.440 --> 32:41.600
I can hear you.

32:42.950 --> 32:45.430
The TV, fridge, and microwave

32:45.460 --> 32:47.460
were all bought less than a year ago.

32:47.910 --> 32:49.530
The curtains were replaced
earlier this year.

32:49.530 --> 32:50.860
They do look quite new.

32:52.280 --> 32:53.810
This is the master bedroom.

32:55.770 --> 32:57.370
It's where I'm living now.

32:57.390 --> 32:59.050
The attic is a separate space.

32:59.880 --> 33:01.510
It's here.

33:07.000 --> 33:09.880
Doesn't the attic
get quite cold in winter?

33:10.380 --> 33:11.140
I...

33:11.170 --> 33:12.430
get allergies easily.

33:12.470 --> 33:14.600
I need to get some sunlight regularly.

33:14.750 --> 33:15.510
This...

33:16.370 --> 33:18.030
There's a small balcony over there.

33:18.030 --> 33:20.760
In winter, sitting in the sun for a bit
feels nice.

33:23.270 --> 33:25.800
The walls look a little yellowed.

33:26.370 --> 33:28.130
Well, this house is quite old,

33:28.160 --> 33:29.310
so it's normal.

33:29.510 --> 33:30.680
If it bothers you,

33:30.680 --> 33:32.320
I can hire someone to repaint it.

33:32.320 --> 33:32.840
Okay.

33:35.020 --> 33:36.260
This is the bathroom.

33:36.350 --> 33:38.160
All the drainage and waterproofing systems

33:38.160 --> 33:39.160
are excellent.

33:39.460 --> 33:40.170
In this area,

33:40.170 --> 33:42.480
it's rare to find an attic
with its own private bathroom.

33:42.480 --> 33:43.270
True.

33:43.730 --> 33:44.970
It's just that...

33:47.240 --> 33:48.680
it's a bit small.

33:49.010 --> 33:49.860
Small?

33:53.680 --> 33:55.030
And this window

33:55.030 --> 33:57.750
directly faces the lane intersection,

33:59.830 --> 34:00.760
which isn't great.

34:00.760 --> 34:02.890
From a fengshui point of view, it's...

34:02.920 --> 34:04.440
not considered very lucky.

34:04.440 --> 34:06.770
I'm already feeling a bit uncomfortable.

34:08.170 --> 34:10.000
I didn't know you knew these things.

34:10.000 --> 34:10.800
Just a little.

34:13.190 --> 34:14.440
I'll get you some water.

34:14.440 --> 34:15.400
Take your time looking.

34:15.400 --> 34:16.199
Okay, thanks.

34:23.210 --> 34:23.920
She went downstairs.

34:23.920 --> 34:26.520
What else do you want to see?
I'll send it to you.

34:27.389 --> 34:28.230
It looks fine.

34:29.000 --> 34:30.000
Stop nitpicking.

34:30.070 --> 34:30.920
Let's just rent it

34:30.920 --> 34:31.920
like we agreed on.

34:31.960 --> 34:33.620
I was nitpicking for a reason.

34:33.630 --> 34:35.710
I just wanted to let her know
the attic isn't easy to rent out

34:35.710 --> 34:36.880
so we'd have more leverage
when negotiating.

34:36.880 --> 34:37.880
What do you know?

34:38.270 --> 34:38.969
Did you see that?

34:38.969 --> 34:39.850
Just now,

34:40.010 --> 34:41.770
when she said she was going downstairs
to get water,

34:41.770 --> 34:45.230
that was obviously an excuse.
She couldn't handle it anymore.

34:48.280 --> 34:49.610
It really was an excuse.

34:50.250 --> 34:53.380
She's on the second-floor balcony,
making a phone call.

34:53.510 --> 34:54.550
You heard it?

34:54.960 --> 34:55.960
I did.

34:56.130 --> 34:57.420
He seems unreliable.

34:57.450 --> 35:00.510
Talking about bad fengshui and all that.
It's too much.

35:00.630 --> 35:01.360
He's so picky.

35:01.360 --> 35:03.280
If he moves in,
he'll definitely be trouble.

35:03.280 --> 35:04.740
Should I wait a bit longer?

35:04.890 --> 35:06.840
If I get a female tenant,
I'll feel more at ease.

35:06.840 --> 35:07.970
Exactly. Keep waiting.

35:07.970 --> 35:09.630
Consider today as a practice.

35:09.630 --> 35:11.950
I just heard her mention a female tenant.

35:12.440 --> 35:15.300
Could there be someone else
coming to see the place?

35:15.470 --> 35:16.400
She went inside.

35:22.720 --> 35:23.320
The water.

35:23.440 --> 35:24.070
Thanks.

35:25.920 --> 35:26.590
I'm sorry.

35:26.590 --> 35:28.150
I thought about it,

35:28.180 --> 35:29.120
and I feel a man and a woman...

35:29.120 --> 35:31.120
Should have some basic boundaries.

35:31.360 --> 35:31.950
Ms. Wu,

35:31.970 --> 35:33.780
I thought about it too.

35:34.030 --> 35:35.880
We're not related or friends.

35:35.880 --> 35:37.880
Even if we live on different floors,

35:37.900 --> 35:39.400
that would still be inconvenient

35:39.400 --> 35:40.110
in many ways.

35:40.110 --> 35:40.960
Right.

35:41.600 --> 35:43.400
So I want to rent the whole place.

35:44.480 --> 35:45.480
Just for 3 months.

35:47.020 --> 35:47.580
What?

35:48.230 --> 35:49.150
Here's the situation.

35:49.150 --> 35:51.660
I was sent to Shanghai
on a business trip by my company.

35:51.660 --> 35:53.630
I'll be returning to Guangdong
in 3 months.

35:53.630 --> 35:54.360
My mother...

35:54.450 --> 35:55.450
is from Shanghai.

35:55.590 --> 35:57.280
I grew up with my grandfather

35:57.280 --> 35:59.000
in a lane just like this one.

35:59.020 --> 36:00.100
When I was a kid,

36:00.130 --> 36:02.150
he used to take me
to the lane entrance to eat those

36:02.150 --> 36:04.880
big pancakes
wrapped around fried dough sticks.

36:07.070 --> 36:07.920
But later...

36:09.960 --> 36:12.360
Later, my grandfather passed away.

36:12.610 --> 36:13.650
So we just...

36:14.480 --> 36:15.290
moved away.

36:15.880 --> 36:18.320
I've seen Ms. Hu at the club.

36:18.580 --> 36:19.790
She's quite clever.

36:19.810 --> 36:22.000
The more you talk,
the more likely you'll slip up.

36:22.000 --> 36:22.840
So,

36:23.710 --> 36:25.190
since I have this opportunity
to come back,

36:25.190 --> 36:25.920
I just

36:26.460 --> 36:29.230
really want to live in a lane for a while

36:30.070 --> 36:31.600
to reminisce about my childhood.

36:31.600 --> 36:33.730
Mr. Gong, stop the drama.

36:33.850 --> 36:34.780
Get to the point.

36:34.910 --> 36:35.470
Shut up.

36:37.310 --> 36:38.570
I didn't say anything.

36:42.220 --> 36:44.010
Well, I totally understand

36:44.230 --> 36:45.920
why you want to live here.

36:46.630 --> 36:48.110
It's just that I have too much stuff.

36:48.110 --> 36:50.230
Moving would be very troublesome.

36:51.400 --> 36:51.960
Ms. Wu,

36:52.210 --> 36:53.630
you didn't get what I meant.

36:53.630 --> 36:54.920
I'll still live on this floor,

36:54.920 --> 36:56.220
and you can lock your bedroom.

36:56.220 --> 36:57.680
I won't touch your things.

36:59.730 --> 37:01.640
But the walls...

37:01.670 --> 37:02.870
I'm not a clean freak.

37:03.800 --> 37:04.920
This bathroom is too small.

37:04.920 --> 37:05.550
You can use...

37:05.550 --> 37:06.280
I'll just use this one.

37:06.280 --> 37:07.590
As long as there's hot water.

37:07.590 --> 37:08.710
This window faces...

37:08.710 --> 37:09.800
It's bad fengshui,

37:09.910 --> 37:10.790
but I'm tough.

37:12.380 --> 37:12.930
Well, in winter...

37:12.930 --> 37:13.600
Ms. Wu,

37:13.740 --> 37:15.380
let me be straightforward.

37:15.750 --> 37:17.230
All those issues I just pointed out...

37:17.230 --> 37:19.230
were just to make sure
you don't refuse to rent it to me.

37:19.230 --> 37:20.420
If you let me rent the whole place,

37:20.420 --> 37:21.450
I'll pay 18,000 for rent.

37:21.450 --> 37:22.930
Three months. All at once.

37:22.950 --> 37:24.470
18,000?

37:25.090 --> 37:26.540
I know it's a bit of trouble for you.

37:26.540 --> 37:28.540
How about rounding it up to 20,000?

37:30.760 --> 37:31.470
20,000?

37:33.250 --> 37:34.920
Didn't you say
you wouldn't rent it to him?

37:34.920 --> 37:36.080
How did you end up

37:36.110 --> 37:37.760
getting kicked out of your own place?

37:37.760 --> 37:39.170
I've sent out so many resumes,

37:39.170 --> 37:41.040
but everyone who contacted me asked

37:41.040 --> 37:42.320
Since that doesn't work

37:42.320 --> 37:43.450
and I can't get a job,

37:43.470 --> 37:44.970
this is the best option right now.

37:44.970 --> 37:45.610
Besides,

37:45.890 --> 37:46.730
it's 60,000.

37:47.230 --> 37:48.690
The money was deposited

37:48.710 --> 37:50.210
right after I signed the contract.

37:50.210 --> 37:52.340
It was like money falling from the sky.

37:55.580 --> 37:57.470
You won't be staying here
during this time?

37:57.470 --> 37:58.840
Why should I stay here?

38:01.180 --> 38:01.750
Right.

38:02.150 --> 38:03.030
You have someone at home now.

38:03.030 --> 38:04.230
Things have changed.

38:04.360 --> 38:05.360
Of course.

38:07.900 --> 38:09.160
What about your place?

38:09.480 --> 38:10.400
My place?

38:11.080 --> 38:12.740
It's just for 3 months anyway.

38:14.030 --> 38:14.710
Xiu.

38:15.050 --> 38:16.730
If you need money, you can tell me.

38:16.730 --> 38:17.790
I can lend you some.

38:19.550 --> 38:22.070
Zhao, I'm not that broke yet.

38:23.070 --> 38:25.550
I'm just planning to start over.

38:25.760 --> 38:27.510
As a new designer,

38:27.510 --> 38:29.240
I don't make much money a month.

38:29.670 --> 38:31.550
So I need to save whatever I can.

38:32.320 --> 38:34.630
I'm already very satisfied

38:34.630 --> 38:36.360
to have such a generous tenant.

38:36.510 --> 38:38.240
As long as you're happy.

38:39.020 --> 38:40.100
I like this place.

38:45.360 --> 38:47.440
The rent was a bit high,

38:47.460 --> 38:49.740
but you can say
I've successfully completed my mission.

38:49.740 --> 38:50.880
I got the place sorted

